name: COMB
description: On February 2, 2021 a huge compilation of databases comprising some 3.8 billion records, offered on the most prominent English-language forum on the Dark Web by a threat actor dubbed Singularity0x01. As in previous cases of compilation of data leaks, in this case also, the origin of the data is unknown. Moreover, Singularity0x01 mentioned he received some of the data from previous compilations, such as Collection #1-5, leaked in January 2019. The leaked includes email addresses and passwords, most of them are clear-text.
